This past year, I've had the amazing opportunity to study Blue Carbon via a research lab through the EEB program! While COVID-19 has definitely made an impact on this experience and its accessibility, I've had the chance to keep working remotely. I created a blog page about COVID-19 and the impacts it has had to me, a senior undergraduate EEB research student. A special shoutout to Kat, my PhD supervisor, for showing me the ropes!
